<section class="blog-post">
    <h1>Why Quality Assurance is Critical for Success</h1>
    <p>
        Quality Assurance (QA) ensures that products and services meet the required standards before reaching the customer. It focuses on:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Preventing defects through structured processes.</li>
        <li>Improving customer satisfaction with consistent quality.</li>
        <li>Complying with industry standards and regulations.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        Adopting robust QA practices enhances trust and reliability, which are crucial for long-term business success.
    </p>
</section>
